  "body": "# üêû Bug Report\r\n\r\nCurrently in pre-genesis we return the genesis block root instead of a zerohash as the \r\nfinalized root.\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\nIn pregenesis due to how our `chainservice` is structured, we return the genesis block root \r\ninstead of the zerohash as our finalized checkpoint. A workaround was done in witti, to make\r\na special case for genesis. This issue is to track the resolution of the correct behaviour in master.\r\n\r\n### Has this worked before in a previous version?\r\n\r\nNo\r\n\r\n## üî¨ Minimal Reproduction\r\n\r\nPeer a Prysm Node With a Lighthouse Node.\r\n\r\n## üî• Error\r\n\r\n```\r\ntime=\"2020-05-26 22:24:21\" level=warning msg=\"Failed to handle p2p RPC\" error=\"invalid finalized root\" peer=16Uiu2HAmVKjTm3YePQgQLxm3fsfAUVgE58opRHZGDXRNLNsqvzBv prefix=sync topic=\"/eth2/beacon_chain/req/status/1/ssz_snappy\"\r\n```\r\n\r\n",
